	Spit trail    
	 Oklahoma City, Dec. 25 (AP): A trail of tobacco spit has led police to a suspect in at least five burglaries across Oklahoma, police said.      
	Randy Lee Shoopman Jr, 33, was charged after a sam ple of his DNA matched that taken from expectorant left behind at the scene of several burglaries.
                                                                                                                                                                     
